				<p>Each game won give 10 points to the guild (if the player is enrolled in a guild), 10 points to the war points (if a war is raging).</p>
			</div>
			<p class="underline font-medium text-l">War Time</p>
			<div class="ml-1">
				<p>During a war time a member can ask to fight randomly any one from the other guild, if no one of the other guild answer the call after a certain amount of time, the match is automatically won.</p>
				<p>There can be only one "War time" match at the same time, to avoid big guilds to flood small ones.</p>
			</div>
			<p class="underline font-medium text-l">Forfeits & Deadlines</p>
			<div class="ml-1">
				<p>If you don't play friendly games there's no impact.</p>
				<p>If you don't play wat time games or ladder games, it will be automatically lost. </p>
				<p>To cappet the game, you have two days for ladder games and the time negociated between the guilds for the war time games.</p>
